title: Freight starting to leave Operation Stack
text:
Lorries are beginning to move along the M20 but in small groups still Credit: PA Wire Kent Police (UK) @kent_police Follow Freight is leaving #OpStack in small groups regularly. Drivers: stay close & be ready to move forward. Food/drink being distributed all day
